{"tid":665055,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食世界第四辣「魔鬼辣椒」 嗜辣男「瀕死」向警察求救","createTime":"2018-05-14T15:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T08:51:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5954fc0835134ed5e9857abf1eaca1a742361c95","tid":665055,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:07:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180514/20390628\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F20390628&d=ZB1ESaTuGoET0BYUrCG2VeI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=4246912b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F20390628&h=9062c48e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180514/20390628</a><br />\n<br />\n食世界第四辣「魔鬼辣椒」<br />\n嗜辣男「瀕死」向警察求救<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不少人酷愛吃辣椒，鍾情那種辛辣刺激口感。然而嚐辣也要量力而為，否則讓身體構成傷害。廣東佛山高明一名市民近日吃下一種被稱為世界第四辣的「印度魔鬼辣椒」後，身體出現異常反應，幸及時送院才逃離鬼門關。<br />\n<br />\n事發於1日晚上，南先生吃了一種從網上購買的「印度魔鬼辣椒」。翌日早上，他一早騎電動車送小孩到學校。大約7時50分，他突然全身乏力，呼吸急促，並出現暈厥症狀。<br />\n<br />\n南先生形容自己當時身體狀況：「當時一點力氣也沒有了，當時有一種瀕死的感覺&hellip;&hellip;」當自己感覺快要倒在地上時，看見路口一名正在執勤的警員，遂鼓起最後氣力向對方求救。<br />\n<br />\n救回南先生一命的警員黃巍表示，南先生當時臉色鐵青，低沉吃力地喊着：「我不行了，快送我去醫院」。黃巍見狀，即時讓他伏在自己的背部，再駕駛電單車駛往醫院。經過及時搶救，南先生逐漸恢復神志，現已沒有大礙。<br />\n<br />\n廣東電視台"},{"pid":"1268c60abdda783c1860a7f9a3e23e2c429e159e","tid":665055,"uid":63190,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:11:40.000Z","msg":"渣架"},{"pid":"0c9da7ffa7b0bd2fd26a3fb24a9923bd2bb6a832","tid":665055,"uid":36029,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:16:43.000Z","msg":"淘寶？<br />\n應該唔關辣唔辣事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421561571f209840389ecb5836a8d508d0cc1ad4","tid":665055,"uid":32577,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蟈嗰啲肯定唔係用天然辣椒啦,用啲工業用料溝出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bef9a2cdd334d4db37325f06ddacafb03b072f5","tid":665055,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:33:55.000Z","msg":"惺咁渣GA"},{"pid":"28889d05a7634800bdd7d09d400827e6cb447f23","tid":665055,"uid":3742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T18:11:57.000Z","msg":"會點急救？"},{"pid":"118ab34f2cbf9f2f78586b8c481991885262eaec","tid":665055,"uid":23021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T18:13:42.000Z","msg":"惺咁渣ga"},{"pid":"6b98dab5dcecaf0094cbbfc3fba0ef3d96e9ffd0","tid":665055,"uid":136707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28889d05a7634800bdd7d09d400827e6cb447f23","tid":665055,"uid":3742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T18:11:57.000Z","msg":"會點急救？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T19:22:51.000Z","msg":"洗食道+胃？"},{"pid":"e6ea34cde6e7f954b6bece90e655e9b60474c1a2","tid":665055,"uid":7374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T19:30:23.000Z","msg":"係咪真係會辣死人？"},{"pid":"97d57a89885e3f95c37d3618a68f7b721a659f5c","tid":665055,"uid":83679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T00:52:57.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"b8ec5800b0f1cd70995eff6abbb124c515dd3df8","tid":665055,"uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e6ea34cde6e7f954b6bece90e655e9b60474c1a2","tid":665055,"uid":7374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T19:30:23.000Z","msg":"係咪真係會辣死人？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T03:46:15.000Z","msg":"How a tortoise react to a red chilli...<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=LCTJUdqRw7o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLCTJUdqRw7o&d=ZB1ESaTuGoET0BYUrCG2VeI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=b634a08b\" data